web_snippets: Rene Anthony Andrada Haas (born 1962) is an American executive who has been chief executive officer (CEO) of Arm Holdings plc since February 2022.
René Lacerte is a technology entrepreneur and the CEO and founder of BILL, a leader in financial operations for small and midsize businesses (SMBs).
